<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link147826" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=147826&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F189499-is-after-all-williams-idolizing-or-rather%2Fanswers%2F147826-i-don-t-think-he-s">flag</a>
</div>
