<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58294461"><img alt="Ο σταθμάρχης Φαλλμεράυερ" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1623161759l/58294461._SY160_.jpg" />
